{"tid":889961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國出現多個 藍潔瑛影迷會 發起幕捐","createTime":"2018-11-05T02:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T03:42:47.000Z","uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"00914f21b75dd17da708db5a2dabe22003fcb321","tid":889961,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T02:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181104/photo/bkn-20181104124405453-1104_00862_001_01p.jpg?20181105060401\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181104%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181104124405453-1104_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20181105060401&h=a0238ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藝人藍潔瑛於家中倒斃，至昨日被友人發現，終年55歲，令人相當惋惜！外界一直未能聯絡其家人，藍潔瑛影迷會指曾聯絡曾華倩、羅家英及鄧萃雯等，呼籲幫忙處理其身後事。<br />\n<br />\n今日，影迷會於微博發出聲明，指有騙徒出沒：「昨天今天發現有人發起二維碼捐款甚麼的，影迷會暫時沒有向社會發起任何募捐活動，謹防受騙，如果哪天需要的話會公佈（布）影迷會微博。​​​​」之後更發布一張二維碼圖，並留言：「重新建了個微信群，本來一直有的，只是得知人不在了時就解散了，現在想來我該給喜歡她的人留一個可以寄託的地方​​​​。」 <br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181104/photo/bkn-20181104124405453-1104_00862_001_02p.jpg?20181105060401\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181104%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181104124405453-1104_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20181105060401&h=f83d25c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181104/photo/bkn-20181104124405453-1104_00862_001_03p.jpg?20181105060401\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181104%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181104124405453-1104_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20181105060401&h=791840e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51b7de64d08230061f60013a95740c85ab8ec5cc","tid":889961,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T03:00:27.000Z","msg":"演藝人協會 屌左支那未? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e19384c8d7e06bcc5659b8d67512b629718f7e","tid":